31:39.106 --> 31:43.991
And this source of power is not earthly or political.

31:44.632 --> 31:47.035
It's not financial or economical.

31:47.255 --> 31:52.921
The source of the power within the church is supernatural and spiritual.

31:53.842 --> 31:55.604
It is spiritual and supernatural.

31:55.624 --> 31:59.968
Now, I will be the first to say, I am so thankful to be in a country.

