32:24.983 --> 32:29.087
It's not political, it's not financial, it's not cultural.

32:29.107 --> 32:32.791
The source of our power comes not from below, but from above.

32:33.072 --> 32:35.154
It comes from God Almighty.

32:36.066 --> 32:37.948
It is a spiritual power we have.

32:39.510 --> 32:51.564
This is what Paul says in 2 Corinthians chapter 10, where he says this in verse 3, for although we live in the flesh, we do not wage war according to the flesh.

32:51.744 --> 32:53.406
That's good right there.

32:53.686 --> 32:56.229
