Lay down my preferences, lay down my non-essential beliefs, because I just want by all means possible just to save a few more for Jesus.

37:51.521 --> 38:00.650
Just to get one more into the kingdom, I will do whatever it takes is how your heart's desire around the purpose of God for the world.

