38:19.732 --> 38:28.264
But at the end of the day, what matters more is what we believe eternally more than what we believe politically.

38:29.585 --> 38:35.794
What matters more at the end of the day is what we believe eternally more than what we believe politically.

38:37.090 --> 38:53.706
So you could try all day to get somebody on your political side, but if they are without Christ, get them on your side eternally, to be an eternity with God forever, with you, to tell them about Jesus, show His grace, show His kindness.

